1
00:00:11,430 --> 00:00:16,660
[2012] [After the 8.17 Case]

2
00:00:54,110 --> 00:00:54,520
Good.

3
00:00:57,480 --> 00:00:58,310
Lang,

4
00:00:58,340 --> 00:00:59,300
you're back.

5
00:01:03,040 --> 00:01:04,170
Are you hungry, Son?

6
00:01:04,680 --> 00:01:06,430
Are you hungry? Are you hungry?

7
00:01:06,760 --> 00:01:07,400
Are you?

8
00:01:09,510 --> 00:01:10,110
Wait here.

9
00:01:11,150 --> 00:01:12,310
I'll cook for you.

10
00:01:16,150 --> 00:01:16,640
Dad!

11
00:01:21,150 --> 00:01:21,760
What is it?

12
00:01:38,479 --> 00:01:39,680
Qi Yan is also hungry.

13
00:01:48,060 --> 00:01:48,620
Dad.

14
00:01:52,200 --> 00:01:53,060
I'm hungry too.

15
00:01:57,580 --> 00:01:58,580
Where is Wen Lang?

16
00:01:59,370 --> 00:02:00,780
Where is my son Wen Lang?

17
00:02:06,680 --> 00:02:07,350
Where is he?

18
00:02:08,190 --> 00:02:09,520
Where is my son Wen Lang?

19
00:02:12,120 --> 00:02:12,780
Where is he?

20
00:02:13,310 --> 00:02:14,360
Where is Wen Lang?

21
00:02:14,400 --> 00:02:15,730
Say something! Tell me!

22
00:02:15,810 --> 00:02:16,540
Where is Wen Lang?

23
00:02:16,540 --> 00:02:17,430
Tell me!

24
00:02:22,770 --> 00:02:24,360
He died.

25
00:02:28,360 --> 00:02:29,630
He died?

26
00:02:31,240 --> 00:02:33,150
He was shot dead by the police

27
00:02:36,710 --> 00:02:38,590
when he tried to protect me.

28
00:02:41,470 --> 00:02:42,600
One shot to the head.

29
00:02:43,780 --> 00:02:45,040
He got shot in the head,

30
00:02:47,800 --> 00:02:48,560
and died.

31
00:02:53,480 --> 00:02:55,410
But your other son is still around.

32
00:02:56,270 --> 00:02:57,540
I, Qi Yan, am with you.

33
00:03:06,650 --> 00:03:08,110
I'll take good care of you.

34
00:03:17,790 --> 00:03:18,920
How did Wen Lang die?

35
00:03:20,310 --> 00:03:21,680
Did you kill him?

36
00:05:06,090 --> 00:05:11,780
[Sunsets Secrets Regrets]

37
00:05:12,100 --> 00:05:14,420
[Episode 27]

38
00:05:27,550 --> 00:05:28,310
Qi Yan.

39
00:05:35,560 --> 00:05:36,560
Professor Jiang,

40
00:05:37,270 --> 00:05:38,930
you are always sharp as a tack.

41
00:05:40,000 --> 00:05:41,200
Are you done playing?

42
00:05:41,720 --> 00:05:42,650
Unfortunately,

43
00:05:43,630 --> 00:05:45,159
since you were distracted,

44
00:05:46,310 --> 00:05:47,390
the game already ended

45
00:05:47,390 --> 00:05:48,720
before it even started.

46
00:05:50,020 --> 00:05:51,360
Your sharpness could save

47
00:05:51,360 --> 00:05:52,800
an entire SWAT team,

48
00:05:53,159 --> 00:05:55,810
but not the girl you love dearly.

49
00:06:01,050 --> 00:06:02,250
The game won't be over

50
00:06:02,900 --> 00:06:04,500
in 51 minutes and 48 seconds.

51
00:06:05,950 --> 00:06:06,680
Impressive.

52
00:06:07,270 --> 00:06:08,270
Professor Jiang,

53
00:06:09,160 --> 00:06:11,410
you must've found the tip
I left at your home.

54
00:06:11,410 --> 00:06:13,420
[Jiang Hansheng]

55
00:06:31,800 --> 00:06:33,260
You are still in Jingzhou.

56
00:06:34,390 --> 00:06:36,450
Is this your guess, Professor Jiang?

57
00:06:37,100 --> 00:06:37,890
Try harder.

58
00:06:38,830 --> 00:06:41,830
You are basically throwing away
Officer Zhou's life.

59
00:06:44,750 --> 00:06:45,610
Are you in town,

60
00:06:47,710 --> 00:06:48,740
or the suburbs?

61
00:06:56,840 --> 00:06:58,370
The suburbs then, I assume.

62
00:06:59,560 --> 00:07:00,240
Qi Yan,

63
00:07:01,270 --> 00:07:03,160
you enjoy seeking attention,

64
00:07:03,680 --> 00:07:05,070
but to make sure the game

65
00:07:05,070 --> 00:07:06,600
can go on smoothly,

66
00:07:07,060 --> 00:07:08,810
I bet you would choose a quiet

67
00:07:09,110 --> 00:07:10,310
and remote location.

68
00:07:14,560 --> 00:07:15,690
I don't understand.

69
00:07:16,040 --> 00:07:18,230
[Search Results of Properties
Registered to Wen Lang]

70
00:07:16,720 --> 00:07:18,980
What do you mean
by "seeking attention"?

71
00:07:21,480 --> 00:07:23,540
When children are too young to speak,

72
00:07:24,510 --> 00:07:25,630
they usually

73
00:07:26,190 --> 00:07:26,800
make noise

74
00:07:27,390 --> 00:07:27,990
by crying,

75
00:07:28,800 --> 00:07:31,530
screaming, and throwing things,
so as to attract

76
00:07:31,560 --> 00:07:33,290
their caregivers' attention.

77
00:07:35,159 --> 00:07:35,750
Qi Yan,

78
00:07:36,950 --> 00:07:39,680
you specifically
targeted women in red dresses.

79
00:07:41,070 --> 00:07:43,530
Whose attention
were you trying to attract?

80
00:07:52,890 --> 00:07:53,450
Alright.

81
00:07:54,950 --> 00:07:56,750
Let's set aside the past for now.

82
00:07:57,280 --> 00:07:59,250
Everything you're doing now only serves

83
00:07:59,250 --> 00:08:00,790
the purpose of getting back at me

84
00:08:00,790 --> 00:08:02,050
and avenging Wen Lang.

85
00:08:05,510 --> 00:08:07,240
If I were you,

86
00:08:08,070 --> 00:08:09,070
I would choose a place

87
00:08:09,070 --> 00:08:10,830
where Wen Lang could see.

88
00:08:18,750 --> 00:08:19,880
My guess is correct.

89
00:08:23,940 --> 00:08:24,690
Perhaps...

90
00:08:26,720 --> 00:08:28,720
you're at where Wen Lang was buried?

91
00:08:33,730 --> 00:08:34,590
No, it's wrong.

92
00:08:36,590 --> 00:08:38,190
Then you must be in his house.

93
00:08:44,700 --> 00:08:46,560
Looks like I've guessed it right.

94
00:08:47,320 --> 00:08:48,850
You're in Wen Lang's house.

95
00:09:07,200 --> 00:09:08,200
Professor Jiang,

96
00:09:08,720 --> 00:09:09,980
you are truly amazing.

97
00:09:10,500 --> 00:09:12,100
Really, if there is a chance,

98
00:09:12,670 --> 00:09:14,360
I would love to ask you

99
00:09:14,360 --> 00:09:16,220
about your tricks for reasoning.

100
00:09:16,390 --> 00:09:17,390
Will you teach me?

101
00:09:18,030 --> 00:09:19,630
Let me hear Zhou Jin's voice.

102
00:09:19,800 --> 00:09:20,920
Then I'll tell you

103
00:09:21,440 --> 00:09:22,860
what gave your secrets away.

104
00:09:22,860 --> 00:09:25,190
How are you so sure
that she's still alive?

105
00:09:27,750 --> 00:09:28,680
Jiang Hansheng,

106
00:09:29,710 --> 00:09:32,280
there isn't much time left for you.

107
00:09:36,940 --> 00:09:38,670
A property in the southern suburbs

108
00:09:38,670 --> 00:09:40,080
belonged to Wen Lang.

109
00:09:40,300 --> 00:09:42,320
I found the exact location
of Qi Yan's phone—

110
00:09:42,320 --> 00:09:44,380
Zongsen Beach in Chengnan District.

111
00:09:52,120 --> 00:09:52,920
What is it now?

112
00:09:53,120 --> 00:09:54,850
Has something happened again?

113
00:09:55,080 --> 00:09:56,960
Everything is fine. Don't worry.

114
00:09:57,130 --> 00:09:58,060
I'm here for you.

115
00:10:12,590 --> 00:10:14,360
Come on, let's record this—

116
00:10:14,380 --> 00:10:16,500
the cheerful Officer Jiang.

117
00:10:18,480 --> 00:10:19,880
How is it, Officer Jiang?

118
00:10:20,510 --> 00:10:21,770
Are you feeling great?

119
00:10:23,110 --> 00:10:25,230
As we told you, this is good stuff.

120
00:10:25,250 --> 00:10:26,760
We'd never lie to you.

121
00:10:38,870 --> 00:10:39,960
So beautiful.

122
00:10:42,060 --> 00:10:43,260
What did you just say?

123
00:10:44,600 --> 00:10:45,600
The sunset glow.

124
00:10:47,910 --> 00:10:49,510
It's so beautiful.

125
00:11:29,720 --> 00:11:30,910
The sunset glow

126
00:11:38,390 --> 00:11:40,080
is so beautiful.

127
00:11:44,260 --> 00:11:45,320
The sunset glow...

128
00:11:50,550 --> 00:11:52,440
What sunset glow could be

129
00:11:54,840 --> 00:11:55,910
so beautiful

130
00:11:58,390 --> 00:11:59,870
that you can't forget?

131
00:12:03,240 --> 00:12:04,200
I hate you.

132
00:12:07,640 --> 00:12:09,190
You've never taken me to see

133
00:12:11,360 --> 00:12:13,270
such beautiful sunset glow.

134
00:12:15,060 --> 00:12:16,460
Is that any way to behave?

135
00:12:30,390 --> 00:12:31,240
Hansheng,

136
00:12:33,390 --> 00:12:35,080
look how foolish he is,

137
00:12:36,490 --> 00:12:38,150
for making me dress like this.

138
00:13:14,250 --> 00:13:16,380
How did they get to know about Wen Lang?

139
00:13:17,320 --> 00:13:20,500
Their judgement has never failed again
during all this time.

140
00:13:20,500 --> 00:13:22,980
Isn't it too risky to lure Jiang Hansheng

141
00:13:24,060 --> 00:13:25,780
to this place?

142
00:13:28,390 --> 00:13:29,200
It's Qi Zhen.

143
00:13:30,730 --> 00:13:32,810
Qi Zhen has been with the police.

144
00:13:34,200 --> 00:13:34,830
Young Master Wen...

145
00:13:34,830 --> 00:13:35,470
"Yan."

146
00:13:47,190 --> 00:13:49,460
Call me "Yan."

147
00:13:50,430 --> 00:13:51,150
Yan...

148
00:13:52,400 --> 00:13:54,260
You didn't fear Young Master Wen.

149
00:13:55,650 --> 00:13:57,770
Why are you afraid of Yan?

150
00:13:59,960 --> 00:14:01,170
I just feel...

151
00:14:02,210 --> 00:14:03,610
you're a bit unfamiliar.

152
00:14:09,300 --> 00:14:10,230
You are right.

153
00:14:13,120 --> 00:14:14,320
What did you just say?

154
00:14:15,660 --> 00:14:17,180
I was trying to say

155
00:14:19,030 --> 00:14:21,200
things are not looking up for us.

156
00:14:21,630 --> 00:14:23,270
We're out of helpers.

157
00:14:23,790 --> 00:14:24,320
Well,

158
00:14:25,130 --> 00:14:27,460
if they really track us down
to this place,

159
00:14:28,270 --> 00:14:29,720
how are we going to escape?

160
00:14:29,720 --> 00:14:30,920
Why should we escape?

161
00:14:34,080 --> 00:14:34,940
Are you afraid?

162
00:14:38,630 --> 00:14:40,270
If you are, then leave.

163
00:14:42,440 --> 00:14:43,480
Leave alone.

164
00:15:15,960 --> 00:15:16,890
I'm not leaving.

165
00:15:23,150 --> 00:15:24,060
I knew it.

166
00:15:25,120 --> 00:15:27,190
My girl Qiu Ye is a responsible woman.

167
00:15:28,200 --> 00:15:28,840
Right?

168
00:15:33,700 --> 00:15:35,100
This is an important day.

169
00:15:36,990 --> 00:15:38,720
Why are you wearing this dress?

170
00:15:40,330 --> 00:15:41,160
How do you...

171
00:15:41,980 --> 00:15:43,860
have time to even notice me today?

172
00:15:56,510 --> 00:15:58,710
I've been watching you the entire time.

173
00:16:01,420 --> 00:16:02,350
The entire time.

174
00:16:07,370 --> 00:16:08,770
Put on a different dress.

175
00:16:10,830 --> 00:16:13,310
You know what I'd like to see.

176
00:16:30,700 --> 00:16:32,150
Get a move on!

177
00:16:56,120 --> 00:16:57,520
Your husband is useless.

178
00:16:58,910 --> 00:17:01,110
He won't get to see you for one last time.

179
00:17:09,400 --> 00:17:10,800
What's there to laugh at?

180
00:17:13,400 --> 00:17:15,599
Does it matter
if he gets to see me or not?

181
00:17:16,270 --> 00:17:17,530
However useless he is,

182
00:17:18,640 --> 00:17:20,170
he's still better than you.

183
00:17:24,440 --> 00:17:25,200
Is that so?

184
00:17:25,400 --> 00:17:26,109
Qi Yan,

185
00:17:27,310 --> 00:17:28,590
you really...

186
00:17:29,960 --> 00:17:31,560
can't bear to lose to others.

187
00:17:32,640 --> 00:17:34,320
But you have already suffered

188
00:17:36,170 --> 00:17:38,340
a humiliating loss to Jiang Hansheng.

189
00:17:39,240 --> 00:17:40,500
You're jealous of him,

190
00:17:40,830 --> 00:17:42,110
so you wish

191
00:17:42,240 --> 00:17:43,500
he will end up like you,

192
00:17:44,070 --> 00:17:46,680
a pathetic worm rolling in the mud.

193
00:17:47,400 --> 00:17:48,960
You want to drag him down so badly

194
00:17:48,960 --> 00:17:50,550
that you don't mind
resorting to whatever it takes.

195
00:17:50,550 --> 00:17:52,210
But can that get you anywhere?

196
00:17:52,480 --> 00:17:54,440
No matter what you do,

197
00:17:56,510 --> 00:17:58,040
the difference between you

198
00:17:59,240 --> 00:18:01,440
and Jiang Hansheng will always remain.

199
00:18:02,550 --> 00:18:03,610
That's because...

200
00:18:05,070 --> 00:18:07,680
nobody cares about you.

201
00:18:08,640 --> 00:18:10,680
Meanwhile, he is loved

202
00:18:11,920 --> 00:18:13,000
by many.

203
00:18:14,640 --> 00:18:16,480
Even if you drag him down,

204
00:18:17,750 --> 00:18:19,480
I'll be there at the bottom

205
00:18:20,670 --> 00:18:21,600
holding him up.

206
00:18:22,920 --> 00:18:26,510
Indeed, guilt can't cause you misery.

207
00:18:28,480 --> 00:18:30,510
What truly brings you pain

208
00:18:32,070 --> 00:18:34,160
is your inferiority complex.

209
00:19:01,000 --> 00:19:03,110
Officer Zhou!

210
00:19:03,960 --> 00:19:06,310
You hurt me.

211
00:19:07,440 --> 00:19:11,280
And you must pay a price for it!

212
00:19:17,030 --> 00:19:18,900
Officer Zhou,

213
00:19:19,270 --> 00:19:20,750
where are you?

214
00:19:24,750 --> 00:19:26,480
Where are you?

215
00:19:30,000 --> 00:19:32,040
Officer Zhou!

216
00:19:54,310 --> 00:19:56,200
You found a hideout yet?

217
00:19:56,510 --> 00:19:58,640
I'm coming to find you!

218
00:20:06,150 --> 00:20:07,200
Why are you helping me?

219
00:20:07,200 --> 00:20:08,510
There's no way I can leave.

220
00:20:08,510 --> 00:20:10,640
But I hope you can get my son out of here.

221
00:20:11,520 --> 00:20:12,750
Forget about anything else.

222
00:20:12,750 --> 00:20:13,680
Will you promise me

223
00:20:13,680 --> 00:20:14,750
to help my son out of here?

224
00:20:14,750 --> 00:20:15,640
Where is your son?

225
00:20:15,640 --> 00:20:17,030
The first room by the stairway.

226
00:20:17,030 --> 00:20:18,090
On the first floor?

227
00:20:18,480 --> 00:20:19,810
But I don't have the key.

228
00:20:20,940 --> 00:20:22,670
You have to break the door open.

229
00:20:24,070 --> 00:20:25,070
I'm begging you.

230
00:20:25,200 --> 00:20:27,270
Officer Zhou!

231
00:20:27,640 --> 00:20:28,790
Got a hideout yet?

232
00:20:28,790 --> 00:20:29,680
I'll deal with him.

233
00:20:29,680 --> 00:20:31,240
I'm coming to find you.

234
00:20:33,240 --> 00:20:35,550
Officer Zhou, where are you?

235
00:20:44,030 --> 00:20:48,160
Where are you?

236
00:21:19,350 --> 00:21:20,960
I'm about to catch you,

237
00:21:21,480 --> 00:21:23,160
Officer Zhou.

238
00:21:27,830 --> 00:21:29,140
You betrayed me.

239
00:21:36,640 --> 00:21:38,830
You betrayed me!

240
00:21:39,940 --> 00:21:41,140
Stop it.

241
00:21:41,510 --> 00:21:43,400
Stop all this, Young Master Wen.

242
00:21:46,160 --> 00:21:48,830
I am Qi Yan.

243
00:21:50,000 --> 00:21:52,440
I shouldn't have saved you years ago.

244
00:21:52,920 --> 00:21:54,510
I should have let Wen Hongsheng

245
00:21:54,510 --> 00:21:57,350
beat you and your son to death,

246
00:21:57,790 --> 00:21:59,750
and had you bled dry.

247
00:22:00,350 --> 00:22:03,060
This is how you repay my kindness, huh?

248
00:22:03,720 --> 00:22:04,440
I beg you

249
00:22:04,630 --> 00:22:06,190
to spare my son.

250
00:22:06,680 --> 00:22:07,240
I beg you.

251
00:22:08,590 --> 00:22:09,400
Spare him.

252
00:22:09,660 --> 00:22:10,450
Please.

253
00:22:10,480 --> 00:22:11,280
Please.

254
00:22:11,830 --> 00:22:12,640
Please!

255
00:22:15,920 --> 00:22:16,720
Qiu Ye.

256
00:22:19,310 --> 00:22:21,070
Do you know why I would always forgive you

257
00:22:21,070 --> 00:22:22,930
no matter what mistakes you made?

258
00:22:24,510 --> 00:22:25,840
Because you would never

259
00:22:27,550 --> 00:22:28,790
give up on your child

260
00:22:28,790 --> 00:22:30,550
under any circumstances.

261
00:22:37,350 --> 00:22:38,550
You're a good mother.

262
00:22:56,560 --> 00:22:58,490
But this time, I won't forgive you.

263
00:23:18,440 --> 00:23:19,160
Little boy,

264
00:23:19,250 --> 00:23:19,680
come with me.

265
00:23:19,680 --> 00:23:20,370
I want my mom!

266
00:23:20,370 --> 00:23:22,160
I'll take you to your mom now, okay?

267
00:23:22,160 --> 00:23:22,790
Really?

268
00:23:22,790 --> 00:23:23,790
Really. Let's go.

269
00:23:42,680 --> 00:23:43,790
Back off!

270
00:23:43,920 --> 00:23:45,400
Back off now.

271
00:23:47,220 --> 00:23:48,020
Let him go.

272
00:23:49,070 --> 00:23:51,480
Why should I let him go?

273
00:24:00,520 --> 00:24:02,180
Officer Zhou, what are you...

274
00:24:03,070 --> 00:24:04,270
If you kill him,

275
00:24:05,830 --> 00:24:07,900
I will die right in front of you.

276
00:24:08,440 --> 00:24:09,720
Don't you just want to use me

277
00:24:09,720 --> 00:24:11,320
to threaten Jiang Hansheng?

278
00:24:11,640 --> 00:24:12,640
If I'm dead,

279
00:24:14,550 --> 00:24:16,750
what will you have to threaten him with?

280
00:24:20,070 --> 00:24:22,070
You will lose completely.

281
00:25:03,160 --> 00:25:04,820
Report to the command center:

282
00:25:04,920 --> 00:25:07,230
The surveillance team has reached
the outer perimeter of the villa.

283
00:25:07,230 --> 00:25:08,030
Report:

284
00:25:08,350 --> 00:25:10,510
We have visual on the first floor.
It's clear.

285
00:25:10,510 --> 00:25:11,170
Roger that.

286
00:25:11,270 --> 00:25:13,310
Sniper point 2, report in.

287
00:25:13,840 --> 00:25:14,360
Report:

288
00:25:14,720 --> 00:25:16,180
Curtains on the second and third floors
are drawn.

289
00:25:16,180 --> 00:25:17,840
Unable to locate the suspect.

290
00:25:18,110 --> 00:25:18,710
Chief Tan,

291
00:25:19,070 --> 00:25:20,410
since the villa backs onto the sea,

292
00:25:20,410 --> 00:25:21,590
there's no way we can acquire

293
00:25:21,590 --> 00:25:23,440
useful information
on the inside the villa.

294
00:25:23,440 --> 00:25:24,240
Deploy a drone

295
00:25:24,440 --> 00:25:25,640
to observe in the air.

296
00:25:25,640 --> 00:25:26,160
Yes.

297
00:25:49,350 --> 00:25:50,080
I'm here now.

298
00:25:51,590 --> 00:25:53,320
You're late, Professor Jiang.

299
00:25:55,130 --> 00:25:56,130
Where is Zhou Jin?

300
00:25:56,590 --> 00:25:58,440
Would you like to hear her voice?

301
00:25:59,750 --> 00:26:01,510
Go away! Don't touch me!

302
00:26:13,840 --> 00:26:14,900
Are you satisfied?

303
00:26:15,850 --> 00:26:16,570
Qi Yan,

304
00:26:17,830 --> 00:26:19,960
Zhou Jin is your only bargaining chip.

305
00:26:20,240 --> 00:26:21,980
Don't blow your chance to negotiate.

306
00:26:21,980 --> 00:26:23,190
Rest assured. As I said,

307
00:26:23,190 --> 00:26:24,590
the game has just begun.

308
00:26:26,240 --> 00:26:27,500
If we are to negotiate,

309
00:26:28,000 --> 00:26:29,920
a face-to-face meeting is more sincere.

310
00:26:29,920 --> 00:26:31,320
Right, Professor Jiang?

311
00:26:32,400 --> 00:26:33,730
I'll be waiting for you.

312
00:26:34,690 --> 00:26:35,380
By the way,

313
00:26:36,110 --> 00:26:38,110
if you want to bring in someone else,

314
00:26:38,540 --> 00:26:39,820
go ahead and try.

315
00:26:40,650 --> 00:26:44,800
I promise they will be surprised.

316
00:26:54,350 --> 00:26:56,280
The situation inside the building

317
00:26:56,920 --> 00:26:58,450
is completely unclear now.

318
00:26:58,720 --> 00:26:59,590
What is Qi Yan

319
00:26:59,790 --> 00:27:00,790
up to?

320
00:27:01,720 --> 00:27:02,920
Is Zhou Jin safe?

321
00:27:04,000 --> 00:27:05,660
We don't know the answers yet.

322
00:27:06,480 --> 00:27:08,350
There are too many uncertainties.

323
00:27:08,350 --> 00:27:09,610
Rushing into the villa

324
00:27:10,310 --> 00:27:11,570
will put you in danger.

325
00:27:12,720 --> 00:27:15,650
But the danger will multiply
if we keep waiting here.

326
00:27:16,270 --> 00:27:17,680
Qi Yan has been timing me.

327
00:27:18,240 --> 00:27:20,350
I have to get in there
now that I've arrived.

328
00:27:20,350 --> 00:27:20,960
Chief Tan,

329
00:27:21,510 --> 00:27:22,590
he asked to meet me alone.

330
00:27:22,590 --> 00:27:24,320
I'm sure he has his own demands.

331
00:27:24,750 --> 00:27:26,880
He has nothing else to threaten me with.

332
00:27:26,880 --> 00:27:27,880
Without Zhou Jin,

333
00:27:28,110 --> 00:27:29,170
he has no leverage.

334
00:27:29,590 --> 00:27:32,650
"If you want to bring in someone else,
go ahead and try."

335
00:27:33,050 --> 00:27:33,850
I think

336
00:27:34,820 --> 00:27:36,680
we are left with no other options.

337
00:27:38,000 --> 00:27:39,000
Professor Jiang,

338
00:27:39,160 --> 00:27:40,420
after you get in there,

339
00:27:40,510 --> 00:27:41,750
try to quickly confirm

340
00:27:41,750 --> 00:27:42,550
where Zhou Jin

341
00:27:42,920 --> 00:27:43,920
and Qi Yan are.

342
00:27:44,640 --> 00:27:45,370
Think of a way

343
00:27:45,960 --> 00:27:47,510
to soothe Qi Yan's emotions.

344
00:27:47,510 --> 00:27:49,070
Just say yes to whatever conditions

345
00:27:49,070 --> 00:27:49,790
he makes

346
00:27:50,750 --> 00:27:51,720
to buy us time

347
00:27:51,880 --> 00:27:52,740
for the rescue.

348
00:27:53,900 --> 00:27:54,740
Don't worry.

349
00:27:55,820 --> 00:27:57,680
We won't take any reckless action

350
00:27:58,070 --> 00:27:59,930
until we're sure Zhou Jin is safe.

351
00:28:00,350 --> 00:28:01,070
You must...

352
00:28:02,470 --> 00:28:04,130
bring her home safe and sound.

353
00:28:05,680 --> 00:28:06,240
Got it.

354
00:28:15,270 --> 00:28:16,600
It all hinges on you now.

355
00:28:37,480 --> 00:28:38,280
Action Team 1,

356
00:28:38,880 --> 00:28:41,110
make sure Professor Jiang is safe.

357
00:28:41,680 --> 00:28:43,160
Stay well hidden,

358
00:28:43,160 --> 00:28:43,830
and try your best

359
00:28:43,830 --> 00:28:45,160
to keep him in sight.

360
00:28:45,960 --> 00:28:46,620
Roger that.

361
00:28:46,880 --> 00:28:50,200
Deputy head of the Provincial Bureau's
Criminal Investigation Department,

362
00:28:50,200 --> 00:28:51,440
Liu Zishan, has arrived on site.

363
00:28:51,440 --> 00:28:52,840
If any emergency arises,

364
00:28:53,010 --> 00:28:54,300
obey Commander Liu's orders

365
00:28:54,300 --> 00:28:55,830
as the highest directives.

366
00:29:14,390 --> 00:29:16,590
A surveillance camera at the entrance.

367
00:29:21,660 --> 00:29:22,420
Qi Yan!

368
00:29:23,790 --> 00:29:24,650
I'm already in.

369
00:29:26,070 --> 00:29:26,870
Where are you?

370
00:29:47,550 --> 00:29:48,960
Report to the command center:

371
00:29:48,960 --> 00:29:51,360
Professor Jiang is in observation point 1.

372
00:30:18,710 --> 00:30:19,230
Report:

373
00:30:19,920 --> 00:30:22,320
Professor Jiang is in observation point 2.

374
00:30:37,110 --> 00:30:38,000
Qi Yan!

375
00:30:41,800 --> 00:30:43,120
Report to the command center:

376
00:30:43,120 --> 00:30:45,450
Professor Jiang has entered a blind spot.

377
00:30:52,640 --> 00:30:53,240
Chief Tan,

378
00:30:53,660 --> 00:30:55,920
I found the stairway to the second floor.

379
00:30:57,350 --> 00:30:58,080
Action team,

380
00:30:58,270 --> 00:31:00,330
try keeping up with Professor Jiang.

381
00:31:05,140 --> 00:31:05,860
Report:

382
00:31:06,130 --> 00:31:08,130
One active camera on the outer wall.

383
00:31:10,030 --> 00:31:11,070
Stay alert

384
00:31:11,070 --> 00:31:12,870
in areas visible to the cameras,

385
00:31:13,330 --> 00:31:14,610
so Qi Yan can see you.

386
00:31:15,080 --> 00:31:16,880
But don't get into the building.

387
00:31:19,400 --> 00:31:20,240
Is there a way

388
00:31:20,790 --> 00:31:22,030
to breach from upstairs?

389
00:31:22,030 --> 00:31:23,090
All first-floor entries

390
00:31:23,090 --> 00:31:24,490
are under surveillance.

391
00:31:24,590 --> 00:31:25,770
I think we stand a higher chance

392
00:31:25,770 --> 00:31:27,430
of breaking in from upstairs.

393
00:31:27,750 --> 00:31:29,200
Then let our men do a free climb.

394
00:31:29,200 --> 00:31:29,750
Okay.

395
00:31:30,400 --> 00:31:31,570
Action Team 1,

396
00:31:31,960 --> 00:31:33,820
get ready to climb over the walls.

397
00:32:46,960 --> 00:32:48,890
Professor Jiang, what's going on?

398
00:33:04,520 --> 00:33:06,450
Professor Jiang, what's going on?

399
00:33:07,130 --> 00:33:08,130
Professor Jiang,

400
00:33:08,160 --> 00:33:09,090
this is Tan Shiming.

401
00:33:09,090 --> 00:33:10,570
Please respond if you copy.

402
00:33:10,570 --> 00:33:11,700
Chief Tan, I'm here.

403
00:33:12,350 --> 00:33:14,240
Surveillance cameras are everywhere
in the villa.

404
00:33:14,240 --> 00:33:15,880
I haven't found Zhou Jin's location yet.

405
00:33:15,880 --> 00:33:16,880
Professor Jiang,

406
00:33:17,350 --> 00:33:19,550
try to locate Qi Yan as soon as possible.

407
00:33:19,790 --> 00:33:21,120
Distract his attention

408
00:33:21,350 --> 00:33:22,950
from the surveillance feed.

409
00:33:23,680 --> 00:33:25,210
We'll find a way to break in.

410
00:33:25,260 --> 00:33:25,780
Got it.

411
00:33:30,100 --> 00:33:31,100
Professor Jiang,

412
00:33:31,930 --> 00:33:33,330
drop your gun

413
00:33:34,090 --> 00:33:35,890
and that walkie-talkie.

414
00:34:03,520 --> 00:34:04,360
Come up here.

415
00:34:05,460 --> 00:34:06,550
I'm waiting for you

416
00:34:06,890 --> 00:34:07,950
on the third floor.

417
00:35:02,000 --> 00:35:04,800
Your girl, Officer Zhou,
had me suffer quite a lot.

418
00:35:11,950 --> 00:35:12,950
Long time no see,

419
00:35:14,240 --> 00:35:15,100
Officer Jiang.

420
00:35:16,230 --> 00:35:16,800
No.

421
00:35:18,190 --> 00:35:19,360
I should call you

422
00:35:21,670 --> 00:35:23,000
"Professor Jiang" now.

423
00:35:24,320 --> 00:35:25,520
It's been a long time.

424
00:35:27,920 --> 00:35:29,650
Sit. Let's do some catching up.

425
00:35:52,220 --> 00:35:53,220
Where is Zhou Jin?

426
00:35:53,670 --> 00:35:54,670
Professor Jiang,

427
00:35:57,070 --> 00:35:58,950
when you beg others, act like it.

428
00:36:00,090 --> 00:36:01,450
Between us, there are still

429
00:36:01,450 --> 00:36:02,730
many unsolved issues.

430
00:36:03,550 --> 00:36:04,840
Officer Zhou's matter

431
00:36:06,010 --> 00:36:06,970
can wait.

432
00:36:15,950 --> 00:36:16,950
What do I have to do

433
00:36:17,630 --> 00:36:19,030
for you to let Zhou Jin go?

434
00:36:19,380 --> 00:36:20,310
All you need to do

435
00:36:21,800 --> 00:36:23,800
is answer two questions of mine.

436
00:36:25,190 --> 00:36:26,070
Then I will...

437
00:36:27,580 --> 00:36:28,980
consider releasing her.

438
00:36:29,030 --> 00:36:29,630
Ask away.

439
00:36:30,480 --> 00:36:32,010
Here is the first question.

440
00:36:32,590 --> 00:36:35,240
Years ago,
by the time you shot my brother dead,

441
00:36:37,670 --> 00:36:39,580
had he already surrendered?

442
00:36:42,810 --> 00:36:44,480
Answer my question.

443
00:36:49,450 --> 00:36:50,110
Yes, he had.

444
00:36:51,760 --> 00:36:52,320
Good.

445
00:36:54,150 --> 00:36:55,750
Here is the second question.

446
00:36:56,670 --> 00:36:59,000
Back then, to shield you from punishment,

447
00:36:59,040 --> 00:37:02,440
did Yao Weihai assert strongly
that you were not of sound mind

448
00:37:03,110 --> 00:37:04,370
when you fired the gun?

449
00:37:06,410 --> 00:37:07,160
Yes, he did.

450
00:37:07,710 --> 00:37:09,250
Very good.

451
00:37:10,630 --> 00:37:11,360
These two questions

452
00:37:11,360 --> 00:37:13,110
haunted me for a long time.

453
00:37:14,800 --> 00:37:16,730
Today, I finally have the answers.

454
00:37:22,350 --> 00:37:23,790
What would you have done

455
00:37:24,930 --> 00:37:26,050
if I had said no?

456
00:37:39,070 --> 00:37:40,470
Do you remember that bet?

457
00:37:41,280 --> 00:37:42,320
Do you remember

458
00:37:42,850 --> 00:37:44,310
the days in the warehouse?

459
00:37:45,150 --> 00:37:46,210
I miss them so much.

460
00:37:47,360 --> 00:37:48,890
Professor Jiang, how about

461
00:37:49,440 --> 00:37:50,900
doing one more bet with me?

462
00:37:52,070 --> 00:37:53,600
This time, the wager will be

463
00:37:56,390 --> 00:37:57,840
Officer Zhou's life.

464
00:37:58,180 --> 00:38:00,000
I don't like betting with human lives.

465
00:38:00,000 --> 00:38:01,330
I know you don't like it,

466
00:38:01,450 --> 00:38:02,700
but I do.

467
00:38:03,760 --> 00:38:04,760
Professor Jiang,

468
00:38:05,490 --> 00:38:06,490
your girl

469
00:38:07,220 --> 00:38:08,970
has put on a red dress.

470
00:38:09,960 --> 00:38:11,280
What a gorgeous lady.

471
00:38:13,840 --> 00:38:15,550
She's meant to be the wager.

472
00:38:16,580 --> 00:38:18,040
Come on, Professor Jiang.

473
00:38:18,630 --> 00:38:20,670
We're destined to have this bet.

474
00:38:21,020 --> 00:38:22,620
Play with me again, will you?

475
00:38:23,030 --> 00:38:23,760
I swear,

476
00:38:24,280 --> 00:38:25,760
this time, if you win,

477
00:38:26,280 --> 00:38:28,410
I'll let Officer Zhou go immediately.

478
00:38:29,830 --> 00:38:30,830
What do you think?

479
00:38:33,360 --> 00:38:34,160
Come on.

480
00:38:35,710 --> 00:38:37,370
Just play with me again, okay?

481
00:38:38,590 --> 00:38:40,280
Please, Professor Jiang.

482
00:38:41,800 --> 00:38:42,880
Jiang Hansheng!

483
00:38:43,670 --> 00:38:45,510
Grab your gun!

484
00:38:47,410 --> 00:38:48,050
Qi Yan,

485
00:38:49,510 --> 00:38:50,630
if you want to play,

486
00:38:51,400 --> 00:38:53,000
I'll play along till the end.

487
00:38:53,920 --> 00:38:56,380
But before that,
I need to ask a question too.

488
00:38:56,570 --> 00:38:58,230
Only you have the answer to it.

489
00:39:02,070 --> 00:39:03,550
The knowledgeable Professor Jiang

490
00:39:03,550 --> 00:39:05,810
actually has a question he can't answer.

491
00:39:10,230 --> 00:39:11,280
Why did Wen Lang insist on

492
00:39:11,280 --> 00:39:13,480
handing over the photos to me years ago?

493
00:39:14,360 --> 00:39:16,820
Only you knew
the consequences of this move.

494
00:39:17,400 --> 00:39:19,460
You wanted me to kill him, didn't you?

495
00:39:27,360 --> 00:39:28,360
Professor Jiang,

496
00:39:29,550 --> 00:39:30,670
this is no good.

497
00:39:31,620 --> 00:39:33,480
That sounds like a sinister plan.

498
00:39:33,690 --> 00:39:35,090
It was you who killed him.

499
00:39:35,640 --> 00:39:37,290
What? After all these years,

500
00:39:38,400 --> 00:39:40,100
you're shifting the blame to me now?

501
00:39:40,100 --> 00:39:40,960
You hypocrite.

502
00:39:41,920 --> 00:39:43,650
You not only refuse to thank me,

503
00:39:43,710 --> 00:39:46,240
but also act like
you're taking revenge on me.

504
00:39:48,550 --> 00:39:49,670
A flaw has emerged.

505
00:39:50,150 --> 00:39:51,030
So, Professor Jiang,

506
00:39:51,030 --> 00:39:53,050
do you admit that you were of sound mind

507
00:39:53,050 --> 00:39:55,010
when you pulled the trigger?

508
00:39:55,040 --> 00:39:56,440
Yes, I was clear-headed.

509
00:39:57,230 --> 00:39:59,290
I knew the person I had to kill was you.

510
00:39:59,440 --> 00:40:00,900
But what about you, Qi Yan?

511
00:40:01,190 --> 00:40:02,850
You've killed so many people.

512
00:40:03,030 --> 00:40:04,430
Who did you kill them for?

513
00:40:04,920 --> 00:40:06,520
You showed tons of giveaways

514
00:40:06,560 --> 00:40:08,030
through your habits in crimes.

515
00:40:08,030 --> 00:40:09,560
Every substitute you chose

516
00:40:09,750 --> 00:40:12,390
reveals your incompetence and cowardice.

517
00:40:13,030 --> 00:40:14,710
A person is weighing on your heart,

518
00:40:14,710 --> 00:40:16,840
yet you dare not lay a hand on him or her.

519
00:40:16,950 --> 00:40:18,010
Who is this person?

520
00:40:20,920 --> 00:40:22,960
Don't act like you know me well.

521
00:40:27,470 --> 00:40:28,720
I know who that is.

522
00:40:28,740 --> 00:40:30,060
Shut up.

523
00:40:30,080 --> 00:40:31,740
In fact, I'm luckier than you.

524
00:40:32,960 --> 00:40:34,090
The person I love...

525
00:40:34,810 --> 00:40:35,960
loves me too.

526
00:40:50,760 --> 00:40:51,820
Proud, aren't you?

527
00:40:56,360 --> 00:40:57,820
Zhou Jin is not with Qi Yan.

528
00:40:57,880 --> 00:41:00,150
Jiang Hansheng is trying
to get information out of him.

529
00:41:00,150 --> 00:41:00,960
Jiang Cheng?

530
00:41:01,760 --> 00:41:02,890
Why are you in there?

531
00:41:06,230 --> 00:41:07,490
Report your location.

532
00:41:09,670 --> 00:41:10,410
The third floor.

533
00:41:10,410 --> 00:41:11,810
We are on the third floor.

534
00:41:11,960 --> 00:41:13,490
Zhou Jin is in grave danger.

535
00:41:14,400 --> 00:41:15,960
The hostage is not with the suspect.

536
00:41:15,960 --> 00:41:17,220
This is not a good sign.

537
00:41:17,410 --> 00:41:20,210
We must quickly confirm
if Zhou Jin is still alive.

538
00:41:20,440 --> 00:41:20,880
Yes.

539
00:41:22,480 --> 00:41:23,360
In this case,

540
00:41:24,710 --> 00:41:26,310
I might as well reciprocate.

541
00:41:28,150 --> 00:41:29,550
Let's talk about Qi Zhen.

542
00:41:31,800 --> 00:41:32,960
What about her?

543
00:41:35,030 --> 00:41:37,160
She said she doesn't hate you anymore,

544
00:41:37,400 --> 00:41:39,600
despite everything you did in the past.

545
00:41:46,360 --> 00:41:48,190
Jiang Hansheng is provoking Qi Yan.

546
00:41:48,190 --> 00:41:49,800
He's probably trying to make him
empty his magazine.

547
00:41:49,800 --> 00:41:50,860
No action until you hear gun shots.

548
00:41:50,860 --> 00:41:51,520
Roger that.

549
00:41:52,920 --> 00:41:54,230
Why would she say that?

550
00:41:54,550 --> 00:41:55,840
Because she is done

551
00:41:56,550 --> 00:41:58,750
hating people and things from the past.

552
00:42:00,070 --> 00:42:01,320
What does that mean?

553
00:42:03,550 --> 00:42:04,550
She and Jian Liang

554
00:42:05,230 --> 00:42:06,680
have their own child now,

555
00:42:07,590 --> 00:42:09,430
a child growing up in happiness.

556
00:42:24,920 --> 00:42:26,070
I don't believe it.

557
00:42:30,590 --> 00:42:32,150
I don't believe it.

558
00:42:32,750 --> 00:42:33,920
Jiang Hansheng,

559
00:42:34,670 --> 00:42:36,070
you're lying to me.

560
00:42:36,920 --> 00:42:39,760
You're lying to me!

561
00:42:48,510 --> 00:42:49,710
Breach immediately!

562
00:42:58,400 --> 00:42:59,280
Leave this to me.

563
00:42:59,280 --> 00:43:00,410
You go find Zhou Jin.

564
00:43:00,710 --> 00:43:01,280
Be careful.
